    %% CONVERSATION DYNAMICS
    subgraph RULES["🧠 RULES OF ENGAGEMENT"]
        direction TB
        R1["Let THEM ask questions — don't fill silence"]
        R2["If they go deep on a topic, LET THEM<br/>Adjust time from later phases"]
        R3["If Amedeo starts selling the vision to YOU,<br/>let him — he's convincing himself"]
        R4["If Corsaro speaks (finally), give him full attention"]
